snippet.title: Highway Police Simulator | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
🚨 Highway Police Simulator | OUT NOW 🚨

Immerse yourself in the authentic police work of the American Highway Patrol. Solve cases, chase criminals and explore the open-world. Choose your officer and tackle the everyday life on the highways. Will you be able to maintain law and order? 

🛒 Links:
🔗Steam: https://links.aerosoft.com/hwps
🔗Playstation: https://links.aerosoft.com/hwpsplaystation
🔗XBox: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/highway-police-simulator/9PJQLDS9PKCV/0010
🔗Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/highway-police-simulator-b0b4a6
